# Privacy Policy

Last Updated: June 2026

## Introduction

Tabernacle is developed and published by Dongo Wongo Games LLC ("we", "our", or "us").

This Privacy Policy describes what information may be collected when you use our games and services.

---

## Information We Collect

We may collect:

- Steam account identifiers and display names
- Multiplayer session information
- Crash reports and diagnostic information
- Gameplay information necessary to provide online services

---

## Voice Communications

If voice chat is enabled, voice communications may be transmitted between players.

Dongo Wongo Games LLC does not record or store voice communications.

---

## Third-Party Services

Tabernacle may utilize third-party services including:

- Steamworks
- Valve Corporation services
- Voice communication services
- Crash reporting services

These providers may collect information according to their own privacy policies.

---

## How We Use Information

Collected information may be used to:

- Operate multiplayer functionality
- Authenticate players
- Improve game stability
- Investigate bugs and exploits
- Maintain game security

---

## Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect player information. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure.

---

## Children's Privacy

Our games are not directed toward children under the age of 13.

